Class browserTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • SearchTestRunner.browserTest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ChromeTest, FirefoxTest

    class browserTest
extends java.lang.Object
    browserTest class contains test steps to be performed. All browser-specific stuff goes to specific classes extending this one.
